<h1>Copying files to/from the reader</h1>
<ol>
 <li><a href="connect-to-computer">Connect</a> the reader to your computer.</li>
 <li>The device will appear in Windows Explorer on the "This Computer" page in the "Devices and Drives" section.<br/>
 Note: the device can then be browsed in a similar way to a computer's disk drives.</li>
 <li>Launch Windows Explorer and locate the file you want to copy. Use the "Copy" command on the file.</li>
 <li>Find the destination location in Explorer and use the "Paste" command there.</li>
</ol>
	

